timeline.message:
Fix issue with using inline fragment inside another inline fragment

For this query we completely ignored `on Human`, `on Droid` nested inline fragments (oops):
```
query TestQuery {
  search(text: "bla-bla") {
    ... on Character {
      name
      ...on Human {
        homePlanet
      }
      ...on Droid {
        primaryFunction
      }
    }
  }
}
```

